						<summary>

						<p>Kāmēśvara temple, central shrine, On the wall behind the <hi rend="italic">dvārapāla</hi> image in the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front, left of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">[Rājarā]ja (I) Year 12.</hi></p>						

						<p>The record is built in all around.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records the endowment by Nāchchi, sister of [Toṇ]ḍaimāṉ, for the food offerings to Periya-pē[ṟu]-mudaliyār in the temple of Tirukkā[mīśvaramuḍaiyār] at Āṟagaḷūr.</p>						

